  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DragonboardGPIOPin
    DragonboardGPIOPin controls an exported GPIO pin on the Dragonboard
    DragonboardIndicatorLED
    DragonboardIndicatorLED provides a means to access the LEDs on the Qualcomm Dragonboard 410c.
    DragonboardLynxDragonboardIsPresentPin
    DragonboardLynxDragonboardIsPresentPin controls whether an embedded Lynx module believes there to be an attached Dragonboard or not.
    DragonboardLynxProgrammingPin
    DragonboardLynxResetPin allows a dragon board to control the programming line of the the attached embedded lynx
    DragonboardLynxResetPin
    DragonboardLynxResetPin allows a dragon board to reset the attached embedded lynx
    DragonboardLynxUserButton
    DragonboardLynxUserButton provides access to the user push button on the Lynx module used with the Lynx / Dragonboard combo.
    TimeWindow
    TimeWindow represents an interval in time on the System nanotime clock
